\c 16
\s Ukugcotshwa kukaDavida abe yinkosi
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSamuweli: Koze kube nini umlilela uSawuli\x + 15.35.\x* lokhu mina ngimalile ekubeni yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 15.23,26.\x*? Gcwalisa uphondo lwakho ngamafutha, uhambe; ngizakuthuma kuJese umBhethelehema\x + 10.1.\x*, ngoba ngizibonele emadodaneni akhe inkosi\x + Hlab. 78.70. 89.19,20. Seb. 13.22.\x*.
\v 2 USamuweli wasesithi: Ngizahamba njani? Uba uSawuli ekuzwa, uzangibulala. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Thatha ithokazi lenkomo esandleni sakho uthi: Ngizehlabela iN\nd kosi\x + 9.12.\x*\nd*.
\v 3 Ubizele uJese emhlatshelweni; mina ngizakwazisa ozakwenza\x + Eks. 4.15.\x*; uzangigcobela lowo engizamutsho kuwe\x + 9.16.\x*.
\v 4 USamuweli wasesenza lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* ekutshiloyo, wafika eBhethelehema. Abadala bomuzi basebethuthumela ukumhlangabeza\x + 21.1. 2 Kho. 4.13.\x* bathi: Ukufika kwakho \add kulo\add*kuthula yini?
\v 5 Wasesithi: Ukuthula; ngize ukuhlabela iN\nd kosi\x + 1 Kho. 2.13. 2 Kho. 9.22.\x*\nd*; zingcweliseni, lize lami emhlatshelweni. Wasengcwelisa uJese lamadodana akhe, wababizela emhlatshelweni\x + Josh. 3.5.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kwasekusithi ekufikeni kwabo, wakhangela uEliyabi wathi: Isibili ogcotshiweyo wayo uphambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 1 Kho. 12.26. Hlab. 14.1.\x*\nd*.
\v 7 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kuSamuweli: Ungakhangeli isimo sakhe lobude besithombo sakhe, ngoba ngimalile, ngoba kakunjengokubona komuntu, ngoba umuntu ubona okuphambi kwamehlo\x + Hlab. 147.10,11.\x*, kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* ibona enhliziyeni\x + 1 Lan. 28.9. Hlab. 7.9. Jer. 11.20. 17.10. 20.12. 1 Kho. 8.39.\x*.
\v 8 UJese wasebiza uAbinadaba\x + 17.13.\x*, wamedlulisa phambi kukaSamuweli, kodwa wathi: Laye lo iN\nd kosi\nd* kayimkhethanga.
\v 9 UJese wasedlulisa uShama\x + 17.13.\x*, kodwa wathi: Laye lo iN\nd kosi\nd* kayimkhethanga.
\v 10 UJese wasedlulisa amadodana akhe ayisikhombisa phambi kukaSamuweli\x + 17.12.\x*. Kodwa uSamuweli wathi kuJese: IN\nd kosi\nd* kayibakhethanga laba.
\v 11 USamuweli wasesithi kuJese: Abafana \add se\add*bephelile yini? Wasesithi: Kusasele icinathunjana; khangela-ke, liyelusa izimvu\x + 17.12.\x*. USamuweli wasesithi kuJese: Thuma ulithathe, ngoba kasiyikuhlala phansi lize lifike lapha\x + 2 Sam. 7.8. Hlab. 78.70,71.\x*.
\v 12 Wasethuma walingenisa. Lona-ke lalibomvana lilamehlo amahle lokukhangeleka okuhle\x + 17.42. Gen. 25.25.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Sukuma, uligcobe, ngoba yilo leli\x + 9.17.\x*.
\v 13 USamuweli wasethatha uphondo lwamafutha\x + 16.1.\x*, waligcoba phakathi kwabafowabo\x + 10.1.\x*; uMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* wasefika ngamandla phezu kukaDavida kusukela kulolosuku kusiya phambili\x + Hlu. 3.10.\x*. USamuweli wasesukuma waya eRama\x + 1.19.\x*.
\s UDavida utshayela uSawuli ichacho
\p
\v 14 Kodwa uMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* wasuka kuSawuli\x + 18.12. 28.15.\x*, lomoya omubi ovela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni wamhlukuluza\x + Hlu. 9.23.\x*.
\v 15 Izinceku zikaSawuli zasezisithi kuye: Ake ukhangele, umoya omubi kaNkulunkulu uyakwesabisa.
\v 16 Ake itsho inkosi yethu kunceku zakho eziphambi kwakho ukuthi zidinge umuntu okwaziyo ukutshaya ichacho\x + 16.21,22.\x*; kuzakuthi-ke lapho umoya omubi ovela kuNkulunkulu uphezu kwakho, uzatshaya ngesandla sakhe ukuze kube kuhle kuwe\x + 16.23. 18.10. 19.9. 2 Kho. 3.15.\x*.
\v 17 Ngakho uSawuli wathi ezincekwini zakhe: Ake lingibonele umuntu otshaya kuhle, limlethe kimi.
\v 18 Omunye wamajaha wasephendula wathi: Khangela, ngibone indodana kaJese umBhethelehema, ekwaziyo ukutshaya, futhi eliqhawe elilamandla, lendoda yempi, lehlakaniphileyo endabeni, futhi indoda ebukekayo\x + 17.34-36.\x*, leN\nd kosi\nd* ilayo\x + 3.19. 18.12,14.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Ngakho uSawuli wathuma izithunywa kuJese, wathi: Thuma kimi uDavida indodana yakho osezimvini\x + 16.11. 17.15,34.\x*.
\v 20 UJese wasethatha ubabhemi, \add ethwele\add* isinkwa, lembodlela yewayini, lezinyane lembuzi elilodwa, wakuthumela ngesandla sikaDavida indodana yakhe kuSawuli\x + 10.27.\x*.
\v 21 UDavida wasefika kuSawuli, wema phambi kwakhe; wasemthanda kakhulu, wasesiba ngumthwali wezikhali zakhe\x + 16.16. Gen. 41.46. Dute. 1.38. 1 Kho. 10.8. Zaga 22.29.\x*.
\v 22 USawuli wasethumela kuJese esithi: UDavida ake eme phambi kwami, ngoba uthole umusa emehlweni ami.
\v 23 Kwakusithi-ke lapho umoya ovela kuNkulunkulu uphezu kukaSawuli, uDavida athathe ichacho atshaye ngesandla sakhe\x + 16.14,16.\x*, ukuze uSawuli avuseleleke abe ngcono, lomoya omubi usuke kuye\x + Jobe 32.20.\x*.